video.title: Sam & Cat
video.synopsis: Roommates Sam and Cat start a babysitting service and soon discover what an adventure the job can be. (One episode of Season 1B is not available.)

episodes.synopsis: When Cat's audition for rapper Peezy B doesn't go well, Sam confronts the rapper to defend her friend and is offered a job as his assistant.
episodes.title: #PeezyB

episodes.synopsis: Cat finds a single pink shoe in a bush. Though it fits perfectly, there is only one, so she and her friends relentlessly hunt for its missing mate.
episodes.title: #MadAboutShoe

episodes.synopsis: As an excuse to exchange gifts, Cat dreams up a new holiday: "Yay Day." But she's not very joyous after she snoops out Sam's gift to her.
episodes.title: #YayDay

episodes.synopsis: After making a bet that "lumpatious" is a real word, Sam and Cat go on a crusade to get their made-up expression into the dictionary.
episodes.title: #Lumpatious

episodes.synopsis: Arrested after Cat takes advantage of a glitch in an ATM, the girls end up in a high-speed chase hot on the heels of a notorious criminal.
episodes.title: #MagicATM

episodes.synopsis: Worried that her old friend Jade will hit it off too well with Sam, Cat schemes to keep her pals apart. But jealousy soon rears its ugly head anyway.
episodes.title: #TheKillerTunaJump: #Freddie #Jade #Robbie: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Cat and Sam escalate their battle by flirting with each other's ex-boyfriends. Can Dice's dangerous tuna fish somehow save their friendship?
episodes.title: #TheKillerTunaJump: #Freddie #Jade #Robbie: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Everyone has become captivated with an addictive new cell phone app. It's all fun and games until it distracts the audience and ruins Cat's new play.
episodes.title: #BrainCrush

episodes.synopsis: While the cast takes a lunch break, they share with fans their favorite bloopers, goofs, mistakes and outtakes from the show.
episodes.title: #BlooperEpisode

episodes.synopsis: Cat and Sam vow to buy a girl a trendy Fresno Girl doll if she excels on a math test, but do they have enough cash to keep their promise?
episodes.title: #FresnoGirl

episodes.synopsis: When Cat gets trapped inside one of Dice's magic tricks -- a box that's supposed to make people disappear -- the gang scrambles to free her.
episodes.title: #StuckInABox

episodes.synopsis: Sam and Cat order items online just to have them delivered by drone, until one of the drones accidentally makes off with a baby they're watching.
episodes.title: #DroneBabyDrone

episodes.synopsis: The girls are hired to accompany two rowdy kids to the Bahamas, but Dice and Goomer's antics cause big trouble at the airport.
episodes.title: #FirstClassProblems

episodes.synopsis: Determined to get revenge on Sam, Nora busts out of prison and kidnaps Dice. Desperate to find him, the girls ask their old nemesis Nevel for help.
episodes.title: #SuperPsycho

episodes.synopsis: After she knocks out a female MMA champ while sparring at Goomer's gym, Sam gets recruited to be an honest-to-goodness MMA fighter.
episodes.title: #KnockOut

episodes.synopsis: After they accidentally knock a rock star unconscious, the girls hold him captive in their apartment while they brainstorm how to get out of the jam.
episodes.title: #WeStealARockstar

episodes.synopsis: When Dice competes to win a hair-modeling gig, Cat tries to prove that another model is wearing a wig, a move that promptly lands her in jail.
episodes.title: #GettingWiggy

episodes.synopsis: When their favorite soda is banned across the state, Sam and Cat start making the sugary drink for themselves -- until the law comes sniffing around.
episodes.title: #BlueDogSoda

episodes.synopsis: Brought together by a crazy mishap in a garbage truck, Sam and Cat become fast friends and decide to start a baby-sitting service.
episodes.title: #Pilot

episodes.synopsis: Sam and Cat take care of a kid who asks a lot of questions and another who always wants hugs; Sam and Cat try to keep their favorite show on the air.
episodes.title: #FavoriteShow

episodes.synopsis: Sam and Cat take care of a goat and try to win over their landlord's son, who wants them evicted; Dice starts managing Goomer, a dumb MMA fighter.
episodes.title: #NewGoat

episodes.synopsis: Sam and Cat baby-sit two British girls who turn out to be con artists; Sam tries to do her school community service requirement at Elderly Acres.
episodes.title: #TheBritBrats

episodes.synopsis: Sam and Cat argue over which one of them is a boy's favorite baby-sitter, and they start competing for his affections.
episodes.title: #BabysitterWar

episodes.synopsis: Sam and Cat take care of Goomer while Dice is away, but they mix up his medications and accidentally leave him blind before his big fight.
episodes.title: #GoomerSitting

episodes.synopsis: A competing baby-sitting service publishes false and malicious comments about Sam and Cat, prompting the girls to confront their new rivals.
episodes.title: #ToddlerClimbing

episodes.synopsis: Cat finds out Sam can write text messages very quickly and convinces her to enter a competition against a boy; Dice tries to avoid an old friend.
episodes.title: #TextingCompetition

episodes.synopsis: Gwen and Ruby pretend to be friendly, but when Sam and Cat realize the con artists are pitting them against each other, they turn the tables.
episodes.title: #RevengeOfTheBritBrats

episodes.synopsis: Cat drinks too much of a special herbal tea meant to help her study, only to wake up later with no memories and Sam's motorcycle gone missing.
episodes.title: #MotorcycleMystery

episodes.synopsis: Goomer's mother has no idea that her son is an MMA fighter, and Sam and Cat try to convince her that Goomer is actually a high school teacher.
episodes.title: #MommaGoomer

episodes.synopsis: Sam and Cat make a commercial featuring Dice's dog, but a family recognizes the dog and seeks legal ownership, saying he was their dog first.
episodes.title: #BabysittingCommercial

episodes.synopsis: Sam opens the safe in her room and finds a tunnel leading to a secret room; Cat films herself for a day to show her future self 10 years later.
episodes.title: #SecretSafe

episodes.synopsis: On Halloween, Sam and Cat are hired to baby-sit a doll, but strange, terrifying things start happening. Cat thinks Dice has been turned into a monkey.
episodes.title: #DollSitting

episodes.synopsis: Sam and Cat take care of an accident-prone kid named Oscar. Even though it'll be hard to keep him safe, they're determined to show Oscar a good time.
episodes.title: #OscarTheOuch

episodes.synopsis: Cat plays a prank on Sam with a pair of twins she's taking care of, so Sam uses her own twin, Melanie, to play a prank on Cat.
episodes.title: #Twinfection

episodes.synopsis: Sam and Cat rename their baby-sitting service to avoid confusion with a TV show, and they track down the show's creators to work out an old grudge.
episodes.title: #SalmonCat

episodes.synopsis: Sam and Cat have to convince a girl they're taking care of to give up her old stuffed toy, but this will be no easy task.
episodes.title: #MyPoober
